parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the biodegradable wiring coating can cause total headlight failure, car fires, and engine fires, leading to dangerous situations and potential accidents.
Electrical system fires can cause damage to the vehicle, injury, or even death.
symptoms: Smoke coming out of the hood
heated seat burning a hole in the seat and clothing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical issues with the convertible top can cause the top to malfunction, leading to safety concerns and potential accidents.
Failure of the infotainment system can cause safety concerns, such as disabling safety alarms and preventing the vehicle from detecting objects near the bumper or sides.
symptoms: SOS light error in the cluster.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to enter limp mode, reducing speed and power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: the transmission warning light is illuminated
the vehicle is unable to maintain speed
the vehicle hesitates or stumbles when shifting gears
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power and acceleration, which can lead to accidents or make it difficult to drive in heavy traffic or uphill conditions.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stumbles when shifting gears
the vehicle slips out of gear
the transmission makes unusual noises or vibrations
the vehicle is unable to accelerate properly.
